    • Field Detail

      • featureResolutionRange

        public final java.lang.String featureResolutionRange
        Range to use when a version is specified on a feature dependency. The default is FeaturesService.DEFAULT_FEATURE_RESOLUTION_RANGE

      • bundleUpdateRange

        public final java.lang.String bundleUpdateRange
        Range to use when verifying if a bundle should be updated or new bundle installed. The default is FeaturesService.DEFAULT_BUNDLE_UPDATE_RANGE

      • updateSnapshots

        public final java.lang.String updateSnapshots
        Use CRC to check snapshot bundles and update them if changed. Either: - none : never update snapshots - always : always update snapshots - crc : use CRC to detect changes
